## Codebase knowledge graph (graphify)
When a graph exists (`graphify-out/graph.json`):
- "how does X work / what calls Y / trace this flow" → `graphify query "<question>"`
- relationship between two things → `graphify path "<A>" "<B>"`
- focus on one concept → `graphify explain "<concept>"`
- Prefer these over broad grep/file dumps. After changing code, run `graphify update .`.

